25:53.083 --> 25:55.219
<v Joe>- It hurts.</v>
<v Andy>- Look, I’ll show you, here.</v>

25:58.701 --> 26:00.051
<v Joe>Told you it hurt.

26:01.739 --> 26:03.830
<v Andy>- It didn’t hurt.</v>
<v Joe>- It hurt.</v>

26:04.725 --> 26:07.486
<v Andy>It didn’t hurt, I was just
pretending, you Bernard.

26:11.394 --> 26:13.405
<v Andy>- Were you filming that?</v>
<v Judith>- No.</v>

26:13.805 --> 26:17.883
<v Andy>Okay, lots of fun, and here we are,
in the Superkings’ garden…

26:18.599 --> 26:21.348
<v Andy>and what is happening today?

26:21.378 --> 26:24.779
<v Judith>We’re digging a pool,
I’m shovelling, Joe’s wheeling.

26:25.271 --> 26:27.845
<v Andy>Okay, and…

26:27.875 --> 26:29.156
<v Andy>No!

26:29.694 --> 26:32.163
<v Andy>Come on! That’s not what you did before.

26:32.506 --> 26:33.606
<v Andy>Now get out!

26:34.580 --> 26:36.253
<v Andy>Now you’re starting to take the piss!

26:36.283 --> 26:38.179
<v Andy>Back. One last time.

26:39.379 --> 26:40.972
<v Andy>You ready?

26:41.002 --> 26:42.283
<v Andy>I’m talking to you, are you ready?

26:42.313 --> 26:43.922
<v Joe>- Yes!</v>
<v Andy>- Right, go.</v>

26:45.334 --> 26:48.737
<v Andy>So, what’s happening today, Angel,
in the garden of the Superkings?

26:48.767 --> 26:52.536
<v Judith>Digging pool, shovelling soil in
