<v Ray>I can’t believe I felt guilty about
getting a promotion over you.

43:47.460 --> 43:50.874
<v Andy>Do you really think that I would
attack somebody for a stupid job?

43:50.979 --> 43:53.329
<v Andy>A mate, I mean, somebody
who I fucking trained up!

43:53.359 --> 43:54.359
<v Judith>What?

43:55.305 --> 43:56.979
<v Judith>You never even got the job?

43:58.860 --> 43:59.860
<v Andy>Come on.

44:00.324 --> 44:02.085
<v Andy>Look, don’t take it out on me.

44:03.785 --> 44:08.068
<v Andy>Look, just think about how you’re going to
feel when they find out who really did this.

44:08.714 --> 44:09.714
<v Andy>Come on.

44:10.503 --> 44:11.503
<v Andy>Mate.

44:11.584 --> 44:12.584
<v Andy>Please.

44:12.788 --> 44:13.788
<v Andy>Please.

44:15.000 --> 44:16.550
<i.action>[voice breaking]</i> <v Judith>Dad…</v>

44:21.329 --> 44:22.960
<v Andy>Why has the music stopped?

44:24.379 --> 44:25.893
<v Sheila>- What was all that about?</v>
<v Andy>- Oh, nothing.</v>

44:25.923 --> 44:29.209
<v Andy>He just blames me because I invited
him out for a drink that night.

44:29.239 --> 44:31.225
<v Andy>- He’s calmed down now.</v>
<v Sheila>- He didn’t look calm.</v>

44:31.255 --> 44:34.008
<v Andy>He was just a bit embarrassed,
I asked him to come back and he said,

44:34.038 --> 44:35.955
<v Andy>well, he just said to
say sorry, that’s all.

44:35.985 --> 44:37.974
<v Andy>Come and have a dance with Andy. Yeah.

44:38.004 --> 44:40.830
<v Andy>- Come on. Come and have a dance with me.</v>
<v Sheila>- No, I’ve done enough dancing.</v>

44:40.860 --> 44:41.860
<v Andy>Come on!

44:42.144 --> 44:43.776
<v Andy>- Alright, Muzzer! Yeah!</v>
<v Joe>- No.</v>

44:43.806 --> 44:45.310
<v Andy>Come on, have a dance with your dad.

44:45.340 --> 44:47.538
<v Andy>Come and have a dance with your dad.

44:47.871 --> 44:49.972
<v Andy>Right, who’ll have a
dance with Andy then?

44:50.002 --> 44:52.359
<v Andy>Somebody’s got to want to
have a dance with Andy!

44:52.389 --> 44:54.474
<v Andy>Come on! All dance with Andy!

45:04.401 --> 45:05.815
<v Judith>For fuck’s sake, dad.

45:07.077 --> 45:08.077
<v Judith>Stop it.

45:19.175 --> 45:20.175
<v Andy>Come on.

45:20.256 --> 45:21.950
<v Andy>Come on, darling, have a dance with me.

45:21.980 --> 45:23.234
<v Andy>Come on, have a dance with me.

45:23.264 --> 45:24.417
<v Judith>Dad, calm down.

45:25.502 --> 45:28.089
<v Judith>Just look at yourself in
the screen, just look!

45:31.328 --> 45:32.814
<v Judith>Look, I understand.

45:35.107 --> 45:36.801
<v Judith>We’ll sort it out, alright?

45:38.850 --> 45:40.829
<v Judith>You don’t have to pretend anymore.

45:46.838 --> 45:48.208
<v Andy>That’s a great idea.

45:49.340 --> 45:50.695
<v Andy>Come play Abracadabra.

45:50.725 --> 45:52.008
<v Andy>Come on, everybody!

45:52.405 --> 45:54.028
<v Andy>Do you all know what you are doing?

45:54.058 --> 45:56.524
<v Everybody>- Yes!</v>
<v Andy>- Yes. Okay, so…</v>

45:56.928 --> 45:58.982
<v Andy>- Everybody in frame?</v>
<v Judith>- Yep.</v>

45:59.012 --> 46:01.686
<v Andy>You’ll like this?
Not a lot, but you will like it.

46:01.954 --> 46:03.137
<v Andy>Okay, so…

46:05.170 --> 46:08.013
<v Andy>Now I shall send everybody to Timbuktu.

46:08.944 --> 46:09.945
<v Andy>Shazam!

46:14.035 --> 46:15.188
<v Andy>Just like that.

46:16.220 --> 46:19.015
<v Sheila>- Right, now what then?</v>
<v Andy>- Now we rewind and play it again.</v>

46:19.045 --> 46:22.198
<v Andy>So everybody inside and let’s
have a look at it on the telly!

46:22.880 --> 46:24.243
<v Judith>Look, dad, no, don’t.

46:24.878 --> 46:27.437
<v Andy>Come on, Angel, we can’t all watch
it on the screen, it’s too small.

46:27.467 --> 46:29.228
<v Judith>Dad, don’t rewind it, alright?

46:29.466 --> 46:31.527
<v Andy>You’re such a spoilsport,
come on, in you go.

46:31.557 --> 46:34.904
<v Judith>I’m not being a spoilsport, just not
with everyone in front of us, okay?

46:34.934 --> 46:35.934
<v Judith>Dad!

46:36.614 --> 46:37.664
<v Andy>Look, Angel.

46:38.814 --> 46:41.489
<v Andy>- Come on, give me the camera.</v>
<v Judith>- Look, dad, don’t play it back.</v>

46:41.519 --> 46:43.673
<v Andy>- What do you mean “don’t play it back”?</v>
<v Judith>- Dad, don’t!</v>

46:43.703 --> 46:45.982
<v Judith>- Not in front of everyone, alright?</v>
<v Andy>- Look, Angel.</v>

46:46.012 --> 46:48.253
<v Judith>Dad, I’m telling you, don’t,
don’t rewind the tape.

46:48.283 --> 46:51.001
<v Judith>- Not in front of mum.</v>
<v Andy>- Look! Don’t be so selfish!</v>

46:51.031 --> 46:53.799
<v Judith>I’m not being selfish, dad,
don’t rewind it, alright?

46:53.829 --> 46:56.146
<v Andy>We’ll get another chance to see
Charlie fall in the pool.

46:56.176 --> 46:58.743
<v Judith>Look, dad, please don’t rewind
it, I’m telling you, don’t.

46:58.773 --> 47:00.373
<v Andy>What has got into you?

47:00.877 --> 47:01.943
<v Judith>Dad! Get off!

47:02.790 --> 47:04.204
<v Andy>Right, where were we?

47:05.192 --> 47:06.519
<v Judith>Dad, it’s a seagull.

47:06.728 --> 47:09.489
<v Andy>No, not there, there!
Not that, that’s a sea–

47:31.977 --> 47:33.782
<v Andy>No-one else will listen to me.

47:37.902 --> 47:39.359
<v Andy>So now it’s your turn.

47:42.286 --> 47:43.960
<v Andy>You one-eyed little fucker.

47:53.072 --> 47:54.882
<v Andy>You made me lie to my family.

47:57.146 --> 47:58.473
<v Andy>You made my wife…

47:59.907 --> 48:01.016
<v Andy>give up on me.

48:03.434 --> 48:04.434
<v Andy>My son…

48:06.044 --> 48:07.044
<v Andy>hate me,

48:08.427 --> 48:10.058
<v Andy>and my daughter betray me.

48:14.742 --> 48:17.286
<v Andy>So have you got any more
tricks up your sleeve?

48:26.089 --> 48:27.503
<v Andy>What do we have here?

48:29.183 --> 48:31.786
<v Andy>Judas Judith, our resident…

48:32.947 --> 48:33.950
<v Andy>snoop.

48:36.358 --> 48:39.032
<v Andy>Come on, love, look at the
camera, no need to hide.

48:40.864 --> 48:43.582
<v Andy>What does it feel like
being under the microscope?

48:46.489 --> 48:48.598
<v Judith>I wasn’t gonna show it to anyone, dad.

48:50.293 --> 48:51.350
<v Judith>I did it for you.

48:51.613 --> 48:53.679
<v Judith>So you could see what you look like!

48:54.822 --> 48:58.627
<v Sheila>Come on, get your stuff together,
we’re going to go into town for breakfast.

48:59.911 --> 49:03.517
<v Andy>Look, I told you, I was just trying to
buy some time to put things right.

49:03.547 --> 49:07.137
<v Sheila>Yeah, well, let’s hope it was
worth £21,000 down the toilet.

49:08.095 --> 49:09.584
<v Andy>I could have sorted it.

49:11.426 --> 49:13.277
<v Andy>Look, I’ll phone the sellers today and
see if they’ll change their minds…

49:13.307 --> 49:14.405
<v Sheila>No, you won’t!

49:14.435 --> 49:16.901
<v Andy>- about the deposit.</v>
<v Sheila>- You won’t phone anybody.</v>

49:17.126 --> 49:19.348
<v Andy>- Oh, come on.</v>
<v Sheila>- No, you come on!</v>

49:20.083 --> 49:21.784
<v Sheila>You’ve already lost us one house!

49:21.814 --> 49:23.896
<v Sheila>There is no way I am having you having

49:23.926 --> 49:26.513
<v Sheila>anything to do with me
trying to save this one.

49:28.702 --> 49:29.899
<v Sheila>Come on, you two.

49:32.747 --> 49:33.747
<v Andy>Judith?

49:34.765 --> 49:35.765
<v Andy>Come here.

49:36.986 --> 49:38.468
<v Judith>- Why?</v>
<v Andy>- Come here.</v>

49:42.907 --> 49:44.799
<v Andy>I want you to answer a question:

49:48.024 --> 49:49.124
<v Andy>Why is it…

49:50.201 --> 49:51.788
<v Andy>that you hate me so much?

49:52.545 --> 49:54.698
<v Judith>- Dad, I don’t hate you.</v>
<v Andy>- No, come on.</v>

49:54.874 --> 49:57.548
<v Andy>What was it that I did
that has made you hate me?

49:58.386 --> 49:59.742
<v Judith>Dad, I love you.

50:02.165 --> 50:03.165
<v Andy>Angel…

50:04.538 --> 50:05.691
<v Andy>Just tell me…

50:07.170 --> 50:08.620
<v Andy>Why do you hate me?

50:11.735 --> 50:13.493
<v Andy>I’m not gonna be angry, just tell me.

50:13.523 --> 50:15.016
<v Judith>Look I understand, dad.

50:16.149 --> 50:17.399
<v Judith>Why you did it.

50:18.810 --> 50:20.461
<v Judith>I know that you did it…

50:22.026 --> 50:23.787
<v Judith>- ‘cause you love us.</v>
<v Sheila>- <i>Judith!</i></v>

50:24.211 --> 50:26.211
<v Judith>I know that, I understand now!

50:27.206 --> 50:29.103
<v Judith>That’s why I did what I did!

50:32.240 --> 50:34.173
<v Andy>- Oh, my Angel.</v>
<v Sheila>- <i>Judith.</i></v>

50:48.846 --> 50:50.651
<v Andy>And there, you see, you have it.

50:52.098 --> 50:54.413
<v Andy>All our sweat. All our…

50:55.552 --> 50:57.886
<v Andy>Blood. All our muck.

51:02.350 --> 51:04.189
<v Andy>Good and bad. Sweet and sour.

51:06.821 --> 51:08.809
<v Andy>It’s a big Kings soup.

51:13.857 --> 51:15.662
<v Andy>And it’s all so simple really.

51:18.634 --> 51:20.660
<v Andy>All you have to do is take it out…

51:22.196 --> 51:23.349
<v Andy>and look at it.

51:29.865 --> 51:30.865
<v Andy>And so…

51:31.552 --> 51:32.748
<v Andy>your fun’s over.

51:34.026 --> 51:35.613
<v Andy>My little filming friend.

51:36.947 --> 51:39.023
<v Andy>No more watching everything.

51:39.683 --> 51:40.844
<v Andy>No more…

51:41.904 --> 51:43.448
<v Andy>storing everything away.

51:44.857 --> 51:47.190
<v Andy>Because now you’re going
to put things right.

51:48.726 --> 51:49.726
<v Andy>You see…

51:50.601 --> 51:52.754
<v Andy>if Judith can understand, I mean if…

51:53.166 --> 51:55.135
<v Andy>Judith can forgive,

51:56.072 --> 51:57.094
<v Andy>Well then…

51:57.745 --> 51:59.750
<v Andy>why can’t the rest of us? Hmm?

52:01.986 --> 52:02.986
<v Andy>You see…

52:04.337 --> 52:06.403
<v Andy>it’s the whole picture that matters.

52:06.745 --> 52:08.642
<v Andy>No more secrets.

52:11.087 --> 52:12.087
<v Andy>And now…

52:13.427 --> 52:15.042
<v Andy>you’re working for us.

52:16.434 --> 52:18.587
<v Andy>And you are going to put our family…

52:19.232 --> 52:20.602
<v Andy>back together again.

52:21.849 --> 52:22.909
<v Andy>Aren’t you?

52:28.252 --> 52:30.200
<v Andy>Alright. Here’s something…

52:31.260 --> 52:32.500
<v Andy>that you think…

52:33.527 --> 52:34.955
<v Andy>I don’t know about.

52:36.859 --> 52:37.881
<v Andy>There we go!

52:39.633 --> 52:40.633
<v Andy>See?

52:41.285 --> 52:46.300
<v Andy>I am not the only one with secrets, am I? Hmm?

52:47.141 --> 52:50.667
<v Andy>Right, now, let’s see
what else we can find.

52:51.929 --> 52:53.169
<v Andy>What did we find?

52:54.381 --> 52:56.645
<v Andy>Well, the answer is, not a lot.

52:57.691 --> 53:00.684
<v Andy>Just a few mementos, but…

53:01.794 --> 53:03.987
<v Andy>here, in an old handbag…

53:04.253 --> 53:05.826
<v Andy>hidden in the lining…

53:07.354 --> 53:09.092
<v Andy>we found this:

53:10.701 --> 53:11.701
<v Andy>It’s Joe.

53:12.336 --> 53:14.532
<v Andy>Look, you can just see his little willy.

53:16.944 --> 53:18.749
<v Andy>But there isn’t one of Judith.

53:18.971 --> 53:21.502
<v Andy>That’s something we need to talk about.

53:23.069 --> 53:24.656
<v Andy>I mean, we’re a family…

53:25.254 --> 53:26.254
<v Andy>a unit.

53:27.194 --> 53:29.192
<v Andy>No room for favourites.

53:30.613 --> 53:33.835
<v Andy>And here, as they say,
is one that I searched earlier.

53:33.865 --> 53:37.787
<v Andy>The lair of the Musby.
A place where daylight never enters.

53:38.942 --> 53:39.942
<v Andy>And…

53:40.687 --> 53:43.839
<v Andy>this is something you didn’t
feel the need to hide away.

53:45.544 --> 53:46.740
<v Andy>And over here…

53:48.168 --> 53:49.264
<v Andy>we have…

53:50.324 --> 53:51.651
<v Andy>cunningly hidden…

53:52.964 --> 53:54.204
<v Andy>What have we got?

53:56.245 --> 53:57.245
<v Andy>Some pills!

53:58.120 --> 54:00.099
<v Andy>And I bet that they’re not aspirin!

54:01.175 --> 54:02.884
<v Andy>And down here…

54:03.691 --> 54:07.626
<v Andy>a phone. And it’s no wonder you wanted
a new one, this one’s so full of film…

54:08.825 --> 54:10.891
<v Andy>there can’t be any room for numbers.

54:11.478 --> 54:14.154
<v Andy>And there’s one very special film.

54:14.730 --> 54:16.238
<v Andy>Starring Joe himself.

54:17.233 --> 54:19.101
<v Joe>Helen fucking Sanderson! Yes!

54:20.572 --> 54:21.572
<v Helen>- Hmm?</v>
<v Joe>- Nothing.</v>

54:29.774 --> 54:31.274
<v Andy>And that’s our bedroom.

54:38.243 --> 54:39.483
<v Andy>We’ve searched…

54:40.125 --> 54:43.601
<v Andy>everywhere in here, except for one place.

54:43.738 --> 54:44.738
<v Andy>And…

54:45.296 --> 54:47.243
<v Andy>where there are padlocks…

54:47.798 --> 54:50.185
<v Andy>there are usually secrets.

54:51.087 --> 54:52.087
<v Andy>So…

54:52.803 --> 54:54.086
<v Andy>let’s just find…

54:55.300 --> 54:56.540
<v Andy>what we’ve got…

54:57.853 --> 54:58.853
<v Andy>in here.

55:02.065 --> 55:03.522
<v Andy>My magic screwdriver.

55:23.021 --> 55:24.261
<v Andy>Honestly, Angel…

55:24.831 --> 55:28.071
<v Andy>if Joe hadn’t have been messing
about I wouldn’t have broken it.

56:58.385 --> 56:59.385
<v Male officer>Hello?

57:01.176 --> 57:02.176
<v Female officer>Mr. King?

57:22.667 --> 57:23.667
<v Andy>Okay.

57:26.200 --> 57:27.361
<v Andy>My turn.

57:35.866 --> 57:37.482
<v Andy>It was me that did Ray.

58:29.234 --> 58:30.236
<v Sheila>Kids!

58:30.755 --> 58:32.688
<v Sheila>Get up! Joe! Wake up!

58:33.337 --> 58:34.337
<v Sheila>Judith!

58:36.228 --> 58:39.430
<v Judith>- What’s happened to the lights?</v>
<v Sheila>- I don’t know, darling. Andy!?</v>

58:40.511 --> 58:41.759
<v Judith>- Where’s dad?</v>
<v Joe>- I can’t smell any smoke.</v>

58:41.789 --> 58:43.029
<v Sheila>No, neither can I.</v>

58:43.144 --> 58:46.297
<v Judith>- Where’s dad?</v>
<v Sheila>- I don’t know, I think he’s still out. Andy!?</v>

58:46.786 --> 58:49.259
<v Sheila>Look, you two wait here, I’ll
go down and check downstairs.

58:49.433 --> 58:51.486
<v Sheila>Joe, see if you can turn
that bloody thing off!

58:51.516 --> 58:52.814
<v Sheila>Just stay there, okay?

59:05.192 --> 59:07.692
<v Sheila>It’s alright, I don’t
think there’s any fire.

59:16.986 --> 59:17.986
<v Sheila>Bollocks!

59:25.910 --> 59:28.106
<v Sheila>Oh bloody hell, who’s moved the candles?

59:29.827 --> 59:31.110
<v Andy>You called for me?

59:31.248 --> 59:32.964
<v Andy>It was me you called for.

59:33.505 --> 59:35.337
<v Sheila>What the fuck’s going on, Andy?

59:36.411 --> 59:38.520
<v Andy>It was me you called for in a crisis.

59:39.641 --> 59:41.287
<v Sheila>What are you talking about?

59:41.317 --> 59:42.467
<v Andy>Oh my love…

59:42.803 --> 59:44.159
<v Andy>you see that fear you’re feeling,

59:44.189 --> 59:48.356
<v Andy>that fear in the dark, I can feel it,
every heartbeat of it.

59:49.200 --> 59:51.440
<v Sheila>You haven’t got a clue what I’m feeling.

59:51.508 --> 59:52.708
<v Andy>Oh, but I have.

59:53.345 --> 59:54.454
<v Andy>I really have.

59:55.408 --> 59:57.001
<v Sheila>If this is another one of your stunts,

59:57.031 --> 59:59.618
<v Sheila>- I swear to God…</v>
<v Andy>- You see, it’s like I knew</v>

01:00:00.283 --> 01:00:01.895
<v Andy>that you would go for Joe first</v>

01:00:01.925 --> 01:00:04.331
<v Andy>when the alarm went off, that
you’d go to save him first.

01:00:04.361 --> 01:00:05.549
<v Sheila>You shit.

01:00:06.007 --> 01:00:07.824
<v Sheila>- You’ve set this up, haven’t you?</v>
<v Andy>- Oh come on…</v>

01:00:07.854 --> 01:00:09.850
<v Sheila>Put the fucking lights back on!

01:00:09.880 --> 01:00:11.538
<v Andy>But we’ve got to face it, Sheila,

01:00:11.568 --> 01:00:14.378
<v Andy>we’ve got to face the way that
we feel about each other.

01:00:14.408 --> 01:00:18.338
<v Andy>It’s like with Judith. It’s not Judith’s
fault that you didn’t want to have her.

01:00:18.368 --> 01:00:21.695
<v Sheila>Don’t twist it, you know what a
state I was in after having Joe.

01:00:22.594 --> 01:00:24.164
<v Andy>Do you know what I realised?

01:00:24.194 --> 01:00:26.494
<v Andy>No, do you know what I realised
when that alarm went off?

01:00:26.524 --> 01:00:28.860
<v Andy>That I wouldn’t have known which room

01:00:29.171 --> 01:00:31.708
<v Andy>to run to first. I couldn’t
have picked between us.

01:00:31.738 --> 01:00:33.717
<v Andy>That fire would have taken us all.

01:00:35.113 --> 01:00:37.744
<v Sheila>You’ve got no idea how I
feel about my children.

01:00:37.804 --> 01:00:39.700
<v Andy>And that’s the point, exactly.

01:00:40.140 --> 01:00:42.945
<v Andy>You know, we’ve got to work
this stuff out, together.

01:00:43.205 --> 01:00:47.971
<v Andy>I mean, really understand the way that we
feel, the way that you understood me, Angel.

01:00:48.852 --> 01:00:49.883
<v Sheila>She’s here?

01:00:49.913 --> 01:00:51.687
<v Sheila>Judith? How did you know?

01:00:53.151 --> 01:00:55.043
<v Judith>Dad, have you got the camera on?

01:00:55.185 --> 01:00:56.599
<v Sheila>Are you filming this?

01:00:57.875 --> 01:00:59.462
<v Judith>He’s got night vision on.

01:00:59.743 --> 01:01:03.716
<v Sheila>- You fucking freak!</v>
<v Andy>- No!</v>

01:01:03.961 --> 01:01:06.356
<v Sheila>- You win, we’re off.</v>
<v Andy>- No, just listen.</v>

01:01:06.868 --> 01:01:08.871
<v Andy>- No, please. Please.</v>
<v Sheila>- You two, get your stuff.</v>

01:01:08.901 --> 01:01:11.274
<v Sheila>Just put something on,
as quick as you can.

01:01:43.587 --> 01:01:48.030
<v Andy>Right, look, nobody’s going anywhere. Just, no,
just go in the lounge and sit down, please.

01:01:48.837 --> 01:01:49.837
<v Andy>Please.

01:01:51.264 --> 01:01:52.764
<v Sheila>- Just get lost.</v>
<v Andy>- No.</v>

01:01:53.146 --> 01:01:55.519
<v Andy>No, look, I just want
you to listen to me.

01:01:56.608 --> 01:01:58.598
<v Sheila>Oh fuck! Where’s the keys, Andy?

01:01:58.628 --> 01:02:01.328
<v Andy>Look, just go and sit down, I’ll give
you the keys afterwards, I promise.

01:02:01.358 --> 01:02:02.973
<v Judith>- Please, dad.</v>
<v Andy>- Look, it’s alright, Angel…</v>

01:02:03.003 --> 01:02:05.612
<v Andy>I just want to show you some filming
that I’ve been doing that’s all.

01:02:05.642 --> 01:02:07.882
<v Sheila>- Yeah, well, tough shit!</v>
